data.description: 21 Space RV park each with 50 Amp, city water and city sewer. Includes 3 bedroom 2 bath home and 1 bed room efficiency apartment and laundry room that make some income. Most every spot is rented. There is also a couple rv's that go with property. There is also a cute courtyard area for guests to sit. This Rv Park is minutes from the Hot water district, Caballo and Elephant Butte Lake. ALL THIS FOR THE PRICE, IT WONT LAST LONG! Monthly income available upon request.
